<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Krista A Dinga Pasalpha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal na semtu te a kiting puou,
 Lalgam panpih ding I um puou maw?
 Kumsawt gawtmun lam chu zuonin,
 Thagau simsen loh a beimang zing ui.

[V2]
 Aw Krista a ding a pasalphate,
 Simsen loh te a man zing lai un;
 Mangthai dingte I puihloh chun,
 Lalpa kawmah bang I gen dem ?
 A thisan mawh I khut ah na ngen in a.

[V3]
 2. Lal nasemtu te a tawm taluou,
 Panpihtu ding guol a ngai nau e
 Panpihtu ding I um puou maw ?
 I Lalpau bangziek a gimthei a him ?

[V4]
 3. Lal nasemtu te a tawm taluou,
 Lalpa Isun nangle a hun sam,
 Khawvel kipahna bei pai ding
 Hun taihsan in Lalpa dingin sem in

[V5]
 4. Lal na semte panpih a ngai ui
 I thil neihteu khawi ah a um tam ?
 Lalpa gama dingin piei tiu,
 A hun tawk nai puoi, a huntawk nai puoi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>262</hymn_number>
</song>